@dev Returns an array of all created auction contracts.
 @return _auctions An array of Auction contracts.

params._duration: The duration of the auction in seconds.
params._increment: The bid increment amount for each bid.
params._nft: The address where the MintNFT contract is deployed to.
params._nftId: The ID of the NFT to be auctioned.
params._startingBid: The starting bid amount for the auction.

getAuctions().details: Returns an array of all created auction contracts.
